<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 06:10:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>未来几年拯救以色列免于崩溃的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-plan-to-save-israel-from-crumbling-in-the-next-few-years/0000018f-ada5-df13-a3af-bdb7f7130000</link><description>“以色列马歇尔计划”将包括将所有有影响力的弥赛亚主义者连根拔起，消除所有吞噬国家资金的正统派和种族主义“反教育”机构，并平等以色列公民的所有权利和义务</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 03:38:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-plan-to-save-israel-from-crumbling-in-the-next-few-years/0000018f-ada5-df13-a3af-bdb7f7130000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨和布林肯谈论拉法，以色列国防军在以色列北部拦截空中目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-live/gantz-and-blinken-speak-about-rafah-idf-intercepts-aerial-target-in-northern-israel/0000018f-ad57-d8a2-a3cf-add7eb670000</link><description>哈马斯欢迎国际法院对拉法的裁决，认为还不够，敦促以色列结束对整个加沙的攻势 ■ 埃及总统塞西和拜登同意通过凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点暂时向联合国运送人道主义援助和燃料 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室称南非对加沙的指控以色列“虚伪、无耻且令人厌恶” ■ 以色列国防军称从黎巴嫩发射了 20 枚火箭弹</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 01:29:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-live/gantz-and-blinken-speak-about-rafah-idf-intercepts-aerial-target-in-northern-israel/0000018f-ad57-d8a2-a3cf-add7eb670000</guid></item><item><title>尽管有灾难警告，以色列南部仍在建设“圣经带”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-bible-belt-is-in-the-works-in-israels-south-despite-warnings-of-disaster/0000018f-ac7a-d8a2-a3cf-acfb5a2f0000</link><description>31 号高速公路沿线在内盖夫的阿拉德和拉哈特之间，规划了 9 个新的城市和乡村地点，其中 4 个指定为宗教社区。严重经济和环境影响的警告被忽视</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 22:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-bible-belt-is-in-the-works-in-israels-south-despite-warnings-of-disaster/0000018f-ac7a-d8a2-a3cf-acfb5a2f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院的裁决并未束缚以色列在拉法的手脚，但以色列必须优先考虑人道主义局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/icj-does-not-order-stop-to-rafah-campaign-but-israel-must-prioritize-civilian-safety/0000018f-ac41-dca9-a5cf-bc41cf8d0000</link><description>国际法院对拉法的裁决并不是停止所有行动的明确命令，但法院明确表示以色列必须将平民安全放在第一位。以色列领导人应该听取法院的意见，而不是努力剥夺法院的合法性</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 21:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/icj-does-not-order-stop-to-rafah-campaign-but-israel-must-prioritize-civilian-safety/0000018f-ac41-dca9-a5cf-bc41cf8d0000</guid></item><item><title>一个对死亡和破坏如此漠不关心的社会已经输掉了战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-society-so-indifferent-to-death-and-destruction-has-already-lost-the-war/0000018f-a53d-d807-a7df-a53fb0370000</link><description>只有那些弱者才觉得有必要释放如此夸张的武力，并对数千名儿童被杀害漠不关心，就像以色列在加沙所做的那样</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 21:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-society-so-indifferent-to-death-and-destruction-has-already-lost-the-war/0000018f-a53d-d807-a7df-a53fb0370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的新叙事：战争就是幸福</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-new-narrative-war-is-bliss/0000018f-abdf-dfc6-a3ef-bfdfb7e60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 19:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-new-narrative-war-is-bliss/0000018f-abdf-dfc6-a3ef-bfdfb7e60000</guid></item><item><title>国际法专家称，以色列司法部门的无能导致了海牙危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/intl-law-experts-israeli-judiciarys-incompetence-contributed-to-crisis-at-the-hague/0000018f-aa55-d8a2-a3cf-aed7d3210000</link><description>专家表示，以色列司法部门在调查违反战争法、高级官员煽动加沙人等事件方面的记录不佳，这将使以色列很难在海牙声称自己正在认真调查。但改变方向还为时不晚</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 18:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/intl-law-experts-israeli-judiciarys-incompetence-contributed-to-crisis-at-the-hague/0000018f-aa55-d8a2-a3cf-aed7d3210000</guid></item><item><title>南非赞扬世界法院对以色列拉法袭击事件的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/update-2-south-africa-hails-world-court-ruling-on-israels-rafah-assault/0000018f-ab95-dca9-a5cf-bf9508690000</link><description>南非国际关系与合作部总干事赞恩·丹戈尔表示，这起案件的重点是加沙的普通巴勒斯坦人，他们现在正面临着第七个月的痛苦，他们因一些与他们个人无关的事情而遭受集体惩罚。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 17:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/update-2-south-africa-hails-world-court-ruling-on-israels-rafah-assault/0000018f-ab95-dca9-a5cf-bf9508690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 231 天：世界法院下令停止以色列在加沙南部的拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-231-world-court-orders-halt-to-israels-rafah-operation-in-south-gaza/0000018f-ab74-d0b4-a3cf-bf7c6ad60000</link><description>国际法院下令立即停止以色列的拉法行动 ■ 以色列国防军称在加沙贾巴利亚找到了三名人质的尸体 ■ 美国众议院议长确认内塔尼亚胡将向国会发表讲话 ■ 拜登：“我们不承认”国际刑事法院对以色列领导人寻求逮捕令的管辖权 ■ 以下是内容你需要知道战争已经过去 231 天了</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 17:08:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-231-world-court-orders-halt-to-israels-rafah-operation-in-south-gaza/0000018f-ab74-d0b4-a3cf-bf7c6ad60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示，它没有、也不会“导致拉法巴勒斯坦人口遭到毁灭”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-says-it-hasnt-and-wont-lead-to-destruction-of-palestinian-population-in-rafah/0000018f-ab45-d24f-a5df-ffe7d84f0000</link><description>在国际法院裁定以色列必须停止对拉法任何可能伤害平民的军事攻势后，以色列拒绝了南非的种族灭绝指控，并表示将继续“依法”允许援助进入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 17:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-says-it-hasnt-and-wont-lead-to-destruction-of-palestinian-population-in-rafah/0000018f-ab45-d24f-a5df-ffe7d84f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队为向英国《每日邮报》提供不为人知的人质绑架信息而道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israeli-army-gave-british-daily-mail-information-on-hostages-kidnapping-unknown-to-family/0000018f-aa2f-d8a2-a3cf-aeaf68c90000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人道歉并表示，“人为错误”是罪魁祸首，此前以色列军队向英国报纸提供了材料，其中载有以色列马坦·赞高克被哈马斯恐怖分子绑架的细节，而该家人此前并不知道这些细节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 11:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israeli-army-gave-british-daily-mail-information-on-hostages-kidnapping-unknown-to-family/0000018f-aa2f-d8a2-a3cf-aeaf68c90000</guid></item><item><title>承认巴勒斯坦国后，以色列外长切断西班牙大使馆与约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人之间的联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israel-cuts-off-spanish-embassy-from-providing-services-to-west-bank-palestinians/0000018f-aa11-df13-a3af-be17e3620000</link><description>外交部长以色列·卡茨表示，以色列将“切断西班牙在以色列的代表权与巴勒斯坦人之间的联系”，以回应西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国以及该国副总理的反犹太主义言论。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 11:01:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/israel-cuts-off-spanish-embassy-from-providing-services-to-west-bank-palestinians/0000018f-aa11-df13-a3af-be17e3620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队打捞出三名人质的尸体，三名人质于 10 月 7 日被杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-recover-bodies-of-three-hostages-held-in-gaza-killed-on-october-7/0000018f-a976-d0b4-a3cf-bf7e034d0000</link><description>军方表示，这三人是在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列领土期间或在他们被带入加沙地道之前被杀的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 09:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-recover-bodies-of-three-hostages-held-in-gaza-killed-on-october-7/0000018f-a976-d0b4-a3cf-bf7e034d0000</guid></item><item><title>受害者和加害者：电影如何让以色列人处理他们压抑的集体创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/victim-and-victimizer-how-film-lets-israelis-process-their-repressed-collective-trauma/0000018f-a8b2-df13-a3af-bcb6c2630000</link><description>以色列电影如何处理该国的民族伤疤？为什么大屠杀和大灾难不断出现在战争电影中？董事们将如何应对 10 月 7 日的影响？</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 04:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/victim-and-victimizer-how-film-lets-israelis-process-their-repressed-collective-trauma/0000018f-a8b2-df13-a3af-bcb6c2630000</guid></item><item><title>“战争让我的妻子想要为在以色列的生活而更加努力地奋斗。我的感觉正好相反’</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-war-made-my-wife-want-to-fight-harder-for-life-in-israel-i-feel-the-opposite-way/0000018f-a898-dfc6-a3ef-bddc1c000000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对夫妇在面对战争时试图决定如何度过自己的生活，而一名年轻人则试图找出如何以他喜欢的事情为中心的日常生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-war-made-my-wife-want-to-fight-harder-for-life-in-israel-i-feel-the-opposite-way/0000018f-a898-dfc6-a3ef-bddc1c000000</guid></item><item><title>“观众比其他人更关心这场冲突”：美联社高级编辑关于加沙战争报道的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/audiences-care-more-about-this-conflict-than-others-ap-top-editor-on-gaza-war-coverage/0000018f-a6b7-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7a0f10000</link><description>美联社正面临 10 月 7 日遇难者家属的诉讼，指控其对袭击事件发出预先警告，并声称其对加沙战争和以色列通讯部长袭击事件的报道存在偏见。在一次内容广泛的采访中，执行编辑朱莉·佩斯反驳了这些指控</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:14:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/audiences-care-more-about-this-conflict-than-others-ap-top-editor-on-gaza-war-coverage/0000018f-a6b7-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7a0f10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府231天的失败。我们到哪儿了？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/231-days-of-failures-by-netanyahus-government-where-did-we-get-to/0000018f-a6cb-d476-a7df-e7eb4b680000</link><description>由于欧洲大门对他和他的妻子关闭，他担心被指控为战犯，这让内塔尼亚胡失眠的时间比人质的命运还要多。 他恳求美国政府把他从海牙救出来，但准备在拜登的演讲背后发表演讲回到美国国会</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/231-days-of-failures-by-netanyahus-government-where-did-we-get-to/0000018f-a6cb-d476-a7df-e7eb4b680000</guid></item><item><title>被俘女士兵的镜头给以色列及其冷酷的总理蒙上了阴影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/footage-of-captive-female-soldiers-casts-a-toxic-cloud-over-israel-and-its-callous-pm/0000018f-a6bc-d24f-a5df-fefec78b0000</link><description>尽管有女兵被扣为人质的悲惨视频，但内塔尼亚胡不会推进协议 ■ 美国现在不再那么反对拉法行动，以色列正在推进 — — 但不是为了击败哈马斯</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/footage-of-captive-female-soldiers-casts-a-toxic-cloud-over-israel-and-its-callous-pm/0000018f-a6bc-d24f-a5df-fefec78b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列已经夷平了这个贝都因村庄的数百所房屋。接下来，它撕毁了所有剩下的东西</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-razed-hundreds-of-homes-in-this-bedouin-village-next-it-tore-down-their-tents/0000018f-a6ed-d1e2-a1ff-aeef40370000</link><description>反对拆除哈利勒干河运动的领导人之一贾布尔·阿布·阿萨说，“当局的行为就像西岸的山顶青年”</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-razed-hundreds-of-homes-in-this-bedouin-village-next-it-tore-down-their-tents/0000018f-a6ed-d1e2-a1ff-aeef40370000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院命令以色列停止任何伤害平民的拉法攻势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-deliver-decision-on-emergency-measures-against-israel/0000018f-a694-d476-a7df-e7fd24770000</link><description>如果以色列违反世界法院停止战争或在拉法的军事行动的命令，它可能会面临国际制裁。尽管美国预计会在这种情况下支持以色列，但大多数西方政府可能会支持法院的裁决</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-deliver-decision-on-emergency-measures-against-israel/0000018f-a694-d476-a7df-e7fd24770000</guid></item></channel></rss>